<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_400" id="199v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Steffan von Abſperg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l2">lantrichter cʒu <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l4">Lıeber her / Stephan / Als 
<del rend="strikethrough">der gegenwertig bote vnſer 
<add><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l3"><expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> guten </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l5">
<del rend="strikethrough">freunde der von Meincʒ bote von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnſer freunde <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l6">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> einen brief </del> ew vnſer <expan>beſunde<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> freunde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l7">die von Meincʒ <expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd bey dem <expan>gegenvvertıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l8"><expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> brief geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Alſo bıten vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erberkeit <expan>fleiſſikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l9">daʒ Jr ew durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache <expan>günſtiklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l10">laſſet <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein / vnd Jn darynne <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd beholffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l11">ſein vvöllet / Als vvir des ein beſunder gut <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l12">ew <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auch allcʒeit v̈mb <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l13">wollen / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthoni Anno xıȷ<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_400" id="199v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Steffan von Absperg, lantrichter czu
                                <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Stephan, als ew unser <expan>besunde<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> freunde, die von Meincz,
                                <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und bey dem
                                <expan>gegenwertige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>bote<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> brief gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        also biten wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erberkeit
                                <expan>fleissikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>, daz ir ew durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                            <expan>günstiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lasset
                            <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein und in darynne
                                <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und beholffen sein wöllet, als
                        wir des ein besunder gut <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> czu ew
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch allczeit ümb
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>
                        wollen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthoni anno xii<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
